y is  6 December , and among the many roles which legend has assigned to him is that of bringer of Christmas presents, in the guise of ‘Santa Claus’ (an alteration of the Dutch form of his name, <i>Sinterklaas</i>)."],"variants":[{"name":"Nickolas","meanings":["Mainly U.S.: variant spelling of   Nicholas  , influenced by the short form   Nick ."]},{"name":"Nicolas","meanings":["From Late Greek.  See  <b>Nicholas</b> ."]}]}],"historicEvents":[{"id":1670191,"age":3,"year":"1700","toYear":"1792","julianDay":2341973,"title":"French Monarchy","description":"The French monarchy started way before the 1700s, but for the most part the major events of history took place during this time before the French Revolution started. This was known as the Bourbon Dynasty. Louis XIV the Great, Louis XV the Beloved, Louis XVI the Restorer of French Liberty, and Louis XVII all reigned during this time.","url":"https://ipfs.io/ipfs/QmXoypizjW3WknFiJnKLwHCnL72vedxjQkDDP1mXWo6uco/wiki/Kingdom_of_France.html","urlTitle":"Kingdom of France","jurisdictionLevel":3},{"id":1670112,"age":81,"year":"1778","julianDay":2370462,"title":"Treaty of Alliance with American Colonies","description":"After the battle of Saratoga France realized that America might be worth backing. They formed an alliance with the colonies and sent naval fleets to help with the war.","url":"https://www.history.com/this-day-in-history/franco-american-alliances-signed","urlTitle":"History-Franco-American Alliances Signed","jurisdictionLevel":3},{"id":1670116,"age":86,"year":"1783","julianDay":2372288,"title":"Treaty of Paris is Signed ","description":"While Benjamin Franklin was the ambassador to France he negotiated with the French during the war to keep them on the American side. At the same time the Treaty of Paris was established.","url":"https://www.history.com/topics/american-revolution/treaty-of-paris","urlTitle":"History-Treay of Paris","jurisdictionLevel":3}],"lifeSummary":"Nicholas Lenning was born in 1697, in Cleebou